      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle stands in pristine, showroom condition, representing the absolute pinnacle of its class. Meticulously maintained and devoid of any discernible wear, it offers a driving experience indistinguishable from its original factory delivery. An uncompromising choice for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection and investment-grade quality.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
